# Autoresearch (Cursor vs Claude)

**Cursor:** run patch experiments via `research_loop` daemon or `autoresearch_orchestrate.py --round N --agent cursor`. Do not hand-edit after DISCARD.

**Claude:** code-shape changes in `autoresearch_train.py` only — see `.claude/autoresearch-delegate.md`.

## Files

| File | Who edits |
|---|---|
| `autoresearch_train.py` | Agents (one hypothesis per run) |
| `autoresearch_prepare.py`, `autoresearch_run.py` | Human only |
| `program.md` | Research org rules |

## Run

```bash
uv run python scripts/autoresearch_run.py cursor
# or daemon: pnpm research:loop
```

Metric: `robust_score` (higher better). **3× KEEP** → tier-2 `pnpm evidence:realtext:research-rag`.

Never enable ASN weight surgery. Log hypothesis in work queue when completing AR-* tasks.
